hadiths[31]{hadithnumber,text}:
2320,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, koi bhi musalman jo aik darakht ka paudaa lagaey ya kheti mein beej boey, phir usmein se parind ya insan ya janwar jo bhi khaatey hain wo uski taraf se sadqa hai. Muslim ne bayan kya ke ham se Aban ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne bayan kya, aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se."
2321,aapki nazar phaalii aur kheti ke kuchh doosrey aalaat par padii. aap ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis qaum ke ghar mein ye cheez dakhil hoti hai to apne sath zillat bhi laatii hai.
2322,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jis shakhs ne koi kutta rakhaa, us ne rozaana apne amal se aik qirat ki kami kar li. albatta kheti ya maweshii (ki hifazat ke liye) kuttey us se alag hain. Ibne-Sirin aur Abu-Saleh ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke waastey se bayan kya b-hawaala Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bakri ke rewad, kheti aur shikar ke kuttey alag hain. abu-Hazim ne kaha Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke shikaarii aur maweshii ke kuttey (alag hain)."
2323,"jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi they. unhon-ne kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha ke jisne kutta paalaa, jo na kheti ke liye hai aur na maweshii ke liye, to uski nekiyon se rozaana aik qirat kam ho jata hai. maine puchha ke kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye suna hai? unhon-ne kaha haan haan ! us masjid ke rab ki qism ! ( maine zaroor Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye suna hai)."
2324,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( Bani-Israeel mein se) aik shakhs bail par Sawar ho kar ja raha tha ke us bail ne uski taraf dekha aur us sawar se kaha ke main uske liye nahi paida hua hun. meri paidaaish to khet jotney ke liye hui hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main is par eman laya aur Abu-Bakar aur umr bhi eman laey aur aik baar aik bhediye ne aik bakri pakad li thi to gadariye ne iska peechhaa kya. bhediyaa bolaa! aaj to too usey bachaataa hai. jis din (Madina ujaad hoga) darindey hi darindey reh jaengey. us din mere siwa kon bakriyon ka charaney wala hoga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main is par eman laya aur Abu-Bakar aur umr bhii. abu-Salma ne kaha ke Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) us majlis mein maujood nahi they.
2325,Ansar ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke hamarey baghaat aap ham main aur hamarey (muhaajir) bhaiyon mein taqseem farma dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar kya to Ansar ne (muhaajireen se) kaha ke aap log darakhton mein mehnat karo. ham tum mewey mein Sharik rahengey. unhon-ne kaha achchha ham ne suna aur qabool kya.
2326,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banii-nazeer ke khajooron ke baagh jalaa diye aur kaat diye. un hi ke baghaat ka naam buwera tha aur Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye sher usi ke mutaalliq hai. banii-Luii (Quraish) ke sardaaron par (ghalba ko) buwera ki aag ne aasan bana diya jo har taraf phailtii hi ja rahi thi.
2327,Madina mein hamarey paas khet dusron se zyada they. ham kheton ko us shart ke sath dusron ko jotney aur boney ke liye diya kartey they ke khet ke aik muqarrara hissey (ki paidaawaar) zameen ka Malik lega. kuchh baar aisa hota ke khas usi hissey ki paidawar maari jati aur Sara khet salamat rehta aur kuchh baar sarey khet ki paidawar maari jati aur ye khas hissey bach jata. isliye hamein is tarah ke mamla karne se rok diya gaya aur sona aur chandi ke badle theka dene ka to us waqt riwaaj hi na tha.
2328,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( khaibar ke yahudiyon se) wahan (ki zameen mein) phal kheti aur jo bhi paidawar ho iske aadhey hissey par mamla kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein se apni beeviyon ko so wasq detey they. jis mein assii wasq khajoor hoti aur bees wasq jo. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apne daure-khilaafat mein) jab khaibar ki zameen taqseem ki to paak beeviyon ko aap ne iska ikhtiyar diya ke (agar wo chaahein to) unhein bhi wahan ka pani aur qat'aa zameen de diya jaey. ya wahi pehli sura baqi rakhi jaey. chunanche kuchh ne zameen lena pasand kya aur kuchh ne (paidaawaar se) wasq lena pasand kya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne zameen hi lena pasand kya tha.
2329,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ke phal aur anaaj ki aadhi paidawar par wahan ke rehney walon se mamla kya tha.
2330,"maine Taaus se arz kya, kash! ! aap batai ka mamla chhod detey, kyonke un logon (Raafe'-bin-Khadeej aur Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) wghaira) ka kehna hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya hai. is par Taaus ne kaha ke main to logon ko zameen deta hun aur unka fayda karta hun aur sahaba mein jo badey aalim they unhon-ne mujhey khabar di hai. aap ki murad Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se nahi rokaa. balke aap ne sirf ye farmaya tha ke agar koi shakhs apne bhai ko (apni zameen) muft dedey to ye us se behtar hai ke iska mahsool ley."
2331,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki zameen yahudiyon ko us shart par saunpii thi ke usmein mehnat karein aur jotein boiin aur uski paidawar ka aadha hissey lein.
2332,hamarey paas Madina ke doosrey logon ke muqaabley mein zameen zyada thi. hamarey yahan tariqa ye tha ke jab zameen jins ki sura mein kiraaye par detey to ye shart laga detey ke us hisse ki paidawar to meri rahegi aur us hisse ki tumhari rahegii. phir kabhi aisa hota ke aik hisse ki paidawar khub hoti aur doosrey ki na hoti. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko is tarah mamla karne se mana farma diya.
2333,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, teen aadmi kahin chaley ja rahe they ke barish ne unko aa liya. teenon ne aik pahaad ki ghaar mein panah ley li, achcha uper se aik chattaan ghaar ke samney aa girii, aur unhein ( ghaar ke andar ( bilkul band kar diya. ab unmein se kuchh logon ne kaha ke tum log ab apne aisey kaamon ko yad karo. jinhein tum ne khalis Allah Taala ke liye kya ho aur usi kaam ka waasta de kar Allah Taala se dua karo. mumkin hai is tarah Allah Taala tumhari us museebat ko taal de, chunanche aik shakhs ne dua shuru ki. aey Allah ! mere waalidain bahut boodhey they aur mere chhotey chhotey bachchey bhi they. main unke liye ( janwar ( charaayaa karta tha. phir jab wapas hota to doodh dohtaa. sabse pahley, apni aulad se bhi pahley, main waalidain hi ko doodh pilaataa tha. aik din der ho gaee aur raat gaey ghar wapas aaya, us waqt mere maan-baap so chukey they. maine mamool (routine) ke mutabiq doodh dohaa aur (iska piyala lekar) mein unke sarhaaney khada ho gaya. maine pasand nahi kya ke unhein jagaaoon. lekin apne bachchon ko bhi (waalidain se pahley) pilaanaa mujhey pasand nahi tha. bachchey subah tak mere qadmon par padey tadaptey rahe. to agar terey nazdeek bhi mera ye amal sirf teri raza ke liye tha to (ghaar se us chattaan ko hata kar) hamarey liye itna rasta bana de ke aasman nazar aa sakey. chunanche Allah Taala ne rasta bana diya aur unhein aasman nazar aaney laga. doosrey ne kaha aey Allah ! meri aik chacha zaad behan thi. mard aurton se jis tarah ki intihai mohabbat kar saktey hain, mujhey us se itni hi mohabbat thi. maine usey apne paas bulana chaha lekin wo so Dinar dene ki sura mein razi hui. maine koshish ki aur wo raqam jama ki. phir jab main iske donon paon ke darmyan baith gaya, to usne mujh se kaha, aey Allah ke bandey ! Allah se dar aur uski mehar ko haq ke baghair na tod. main ye suntey hi door ho gaya, agar mera ye amal terey ilm mein bhi teri raza hi ke liye tha to (is ghaar se) patthar ko hata de. to ghaar ka munh kuchh aur khulaa. ab tesraa bola ke aey Allaah! maine aik mazdoor teen farq chaawal ki mazdoorii par muqarrar kya tha jab us ne apna kaam pura kar liya to mujh se kaha ke ab meri mazdoorii mujhey de-dey. maine pesh kar di lekin us waqt wo inkar kar baithaa. phir main barabar uski ujrat se khetii kartaa raha aur uske nateeje mein badhney se bail aur charwaahey mere paas jama ho gaey. ab wo shakhs aaya aur kehney laga ke Allah se dar! maine kaha ke bail aur uske charwaahey ke paas ja aur usey ley ley. usne kaha Allah se dar ! aur mujh se mazaaq na kar, maine kaha ke mazaaq nahi kar raha hun. (ye sab tera hi hai) ab tum usey ley jao . to us ne un sab par qabza kar liya. Ilaahii! agar terey ilm mein bhi maine ye kaam teri khushnoodii hi ke liye kya tha to too us ghaar ko khol de. ab wo ghaar pura khul chuka tha. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke ibne- Aqba ne Naafe se (apni riwayat main ( فبغيت‏ (ke bajaey) ( فسعيت‏ ( naql kya hai."
2334,"ham se sadqa ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham ko Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne khabar di, unhein Imam Malik ne, unhein Zaid-bin-Aslam ne, unse unke walid ne bayan kya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, agar mujhey baad mein aaney waley musalmanon ka khayal na hota to jitney Shahar bhi fateh karta, unhein fateh karne walon mein taqseem karta jata, bilkul isi tarah jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki zameen taqseem farma di thi. . . . hadis mutaalliqa abwaab : maftooha Shahar ki gaaziyon mein taqseem ki sunnat ."
2335,"jisne koi aisi zameen abad ki, jis par kisi ka haq nahi tha to us zameen ka wahi haqdaar hai. Urwa ne bayan kya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne daure-khilaafat mein yahi faisla kya tha."
2336,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Makka ke liye tashrif ley jatey huey) jab zul-Hulaifa mein naala ke dhaal mein raat ke aakhiri hisse mein padao kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khuwab mein kaha gaya ke aap us waqt aik Mubarak wadi mein hain. Musa-bin-Aqba ( rawi hadis) ne bayan kya ke Salim ( Salim bin-Abdullah-bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bhi hamarey sath wahin oont bithaya jahan Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bithaya kartey they, taake us jagah qiyam kar sakein , jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qiyam farmaya tha. ye jagah wadi aqeeq ki masjid se naala ke dhaal mein hai. wadi aqeeq aur rastey ke darmyan mein."
2337,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya raat mere paas mere rab ki taraf se aik aaney wala farishta aaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt wadi aqeeq mein qiyam kiye huey they. (aur us ne ye paigham pahunchaya ke) us Mubarak wadi mein Namaz padh aur kaha ke keh dijiye ! Umra Haj mein Sharik ho gaya.
2338,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (jab khaibar par) fateh hasil ki thi (doosri sanad) aur Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha ke ham ko ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha ke mujh se Musa-bin-Aqba ne bayan kya, unse Naafe ne, unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne yahudiyon aur esaiyon ko  hijaaz ki zameen se nikal diya tha aur jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar par fateh paai to aap ne bhi yahudiyon ko wahan se nikaalnaa chaha tha. jab aapko wahan fateh hasil hui to uski zameen Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur musalmanon ki ho gaee thi. aap ka irada yahudiyon ko wahan se bahar karne ka tha, lekin yahudiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhaast ki ke aap hamein yahin rehney dein. ham ( khaibar ki araazii ka ( Sara kaam khud karengey aur uski paidawar ka nisf hissey ley lengey. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha jab tak ham chaahein tumhen us shart par yahan rehney dengey. chunanche wo log wahin rahe aur phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein teemaa aur areehaa ki taraf jalaa watan kar diya."
2339,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein aik aisey kaam se mana kya tha jis mein hamara ( bazahir zaati ( fayda tha. is par maine kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo kuchh bhi farmaya wo haq hai. Zuher (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bulaya aur malum farmaya ke tum log apne kheton ka mamla kis tarah kartey ho? maine kaha ke ham apne kheton ko) boney ke liye) nehar ke qareeb ki zameen ki shart par de detey hain. isi tarah khajoor aur jau ke chand wasq par. ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa na karo. ya khud usmein kheti kya karo ya dusron se karao . warna usey yun khali hi chhod do. Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine kaha (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye farman ( maine suna aur maan liya.
2340,"sahaba tehai , chothai ya aadhe par batai ka mamla kya kartey they. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiske paas zameen ho to usey khud boey warna dusron ko bakhsh de. agar ye bhi nahi kar sakta to usey yun hi khali chhod de."
2341,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jiske paas zameen ho to wo khud boey warna apne kisi ( musalman ( bhai ko bakhsh de, aur agar ye nahi kar sakta to usey yun hi khali chhod de."
2342,to unhon-ne kaha ke) batai wghaira par) kheeti kara sakta hai. ibne-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana nahi kya tha. albatta Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha ke apne kisi bhai ko zameen bakhshish ke taur par de dena us se behtar hai ke is par koi mahsoor ley. (ye is sura mein ke zameendaar ke paas faaltu zameen bekaar padi ho ( .
2343,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apne kheton ko Nabi Karim (sl), Abu-Bakar , umr , Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke ahad main aur Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke shuruati daure-khilaafat mein kiraaey par detey they."
2344,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kheton ko kiraaya par deney se mana kya tha. (ye sun kar) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey. mein bhi unke sath tha. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse puchha to unhon-ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kheton ko kiraaya par deney se mana farmaya, is par ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aapko malum hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein ham apne kheton ko us paidawar ke badal jo naaliyon par ho aur thodi ghaas ke badal diya kartey they."
2345,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein mujhey malum tha ke zameen ko batai par diya jata tha. phir unhein dar hua ke mumkin hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is silsiley mein koi nai hidayat farmai ho jiska ilm unhein na hua ho. chunanche unhon-ne ( ehtiyati taur par ( zameen ko batai par dena chhod diya.
2346,"mere chacha ( Zuhair aur muhair (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bayan kya ke wo log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein zameen ko batai par nehar (ke qareeb ki paidawar ( ki shart par diya kartey. ya koi bhi aisa khitta hota jisey Malik zameen (apne liye) chaant leta . isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farma diya. Hanzala ne kaha ke is par maine Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, agar dirham w Dinar ke badley ye mamla kya jaey to kya hukm hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke agar Dinar w dirham ke badley mein ho to usmein koi harj nahi. aur Leis ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jis tarah ki batai se mana farmaya tha, wo aisi sura hai ke halal w haram ki tameez rakhney wala koi bhi shakhs usey jaaiz nahi qarar de sakta. kyonke usmein khula dhoka hai."
2347,"mere chacha ( Zuhair aur Muhair (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bayan kya ke wo log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein zameen ko batai par nehar (ke qareeb ki paidawar ( ki shart par diya kartey. ya koi bhi aisa khitta hota jisey Malik zameen (apne liye) chaant leta . isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farma diya. Hanzala ne kaha ke is par maine Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, agar dirham w Dinar ke badley ye mamla kya jaey to kya hukm hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke agar Dinar w dirham ke badley mein ho to usmein koi harj nahi. aur Leis ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jis tarah ki batai se mana farmaya tha, wo aisi sura hai ke halal w haram ki tameez rakhney wala koi bhi shakhs usey jaaiz nahi qarar de sakta. kyonke usmein khula dhoka hai."
2348,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din bayan farma rahe they. aik dehati bhi majlis mein hazir tha ke ahal-e-jannat mein se aik shakhs apne rab se kheti karne ki ijazat chaahega . Allah Taala us se farmaeyga kya apni maujooda haalat par to razi nahi hai? wo kahega kyon nahi ! lekin mera ji kheti karne ko chahta hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir us ne beej dala. palak jhapakney mein wo ug bhi aaya. paak bhi gaya aur kaat bhi liya gaya aur uske daney pahadon ki tarah huey. ab Allah Taala farmata hai, aey ibne-Aadam ! usey rakh ley , tujhey koi cheez aasooda nahi kar sakti . ye sun kar dehati ne kaha ke qism Allah ki wo to koi qureshi ya Ansari hi hoga. kyonke yahi log kheti karne waley hain. ham to kheti hi nahi kartey. is baat par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hansi aa gaee."
2349,"Juma ke din hamein bahut khushi (is baat ki) hoti thi ke hamari aik boodhi aurat thin jo us chukandar ko ukhaad laateen jisey ham apne baagh ki mendon par bo diya kartey they. wo unko apni handi mein pakaatiin aur is mein thodey se jau bhi daal detin . abu-Hazim ne kaha, main nahi janta ke Sehal ne yun kahaa: na usmein charbi hoti na chiknai . phir jab ham Juma ki Namaz padh letey to unki khidmat mein hazir hotey . wo apna pakwaan hamarey samney kar detin aur isliye hamein Juma ke din ki khushi hoti thi aur ham do-pahar ka khana aur qailula Juma ke baad kya kartey they."
2350,"log kehtey hain Abu-Hurera bahut hadis bayan kartey hain. halanke mujhey bhi Allah se milnaa hai (main ghalat bayaanii kaisey kar sakta hun) ye log ye bhi kehtey hain ke muhajireen aur Ansar aakhir uski tarah kyon hadisein bayan nahi kartey ? baat ye hai ke mere bhai muhajireen bazaron mein khareed w farokht mein mashghool raha kartey aur mere bhai Ansar ko unki jaaidaad ( khet aur baghaat wghaira) mashghool rakha karti thi. sirf mein aik miskeen aadmi tha. pet bhar leney ke baad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat hi mein barabar hazir raha karta. jab ye sab hazraat ghair hazir rahtey to main hazir hota. isliye jin hadison ko ye yad nahi kar saktey they, mein unhein yad rakhta tha, aur aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke tum mein se jo shakhs bhi apne kapdey ko meri us taqreer ke khatm honey tak phailaey rakhey phir ( taqreer khatm honey par) usey apne seeney se laga ley to wo meri hadison ko kabhi nahi bhooley ga . maine apni kamlii ko phaila diya. jiske siwa mera badan par aur koi kapda nahi tha. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni taqreer khatm farmai to maine wo chadar apne seeney se laga li. us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath Nabi bana kar maboos kya, phir aaj tak mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke usi irshad ki wjah se (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki koi hadis nahi bhula ). Allah gawah hai ke agar Quran ki 2 aayatein na hotiin to main tum se koi hadis kabhi bayan na karta aayat ( إن الذين يكتمون ما أنزلنا من البينات‏ ( se Allah Taala ke irshad ( الرحيم‏ ( tak. (jis mein) is Deen ke chhipaaney waley par, jisey Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zariey duniya mein bheja hai, sakht laanat ki gaee hai."
